properties.description:
Farnborough (Yeppoon) – bushfire as at 3.45pm Tue 26 Jan         Queensland Fire and Emergency Services (QFES) advises that conditions have changed on the fireground at the fire near Farnborough. Multiple QFES crews are on scene working to contain the blaze. The fire is burning between Fishing Creek Road and Kelly’s Landing Road and smoke may impact nearby residents in Maryvale, Woodbury and Byfield. Residents are asked to close windows and doors and if suffering from a respiratory condition, keep medications close by. Motorists should drive with caution and to conditions. If residents are concerned their property is under threat, they are advised to call Triple Zero (000) immediately.  
Response Time: 20210114153529
Vehicles on Scene:7
Vehicles on Route: 0
